               AWS -->dashboard -->ASG -- > master/worker node -- > select -->edit -- > desired: 4 -- > save

    
***DELETE CLUSTER:-

            kops delete cluster --name nithya.k8s.local --state=s3://kops-state-file-data1234.k8s.local --yes
            kops delete cluster --name nithya.k8s.local --yes











